'''大卫·布鲁斯·"戴夫"·戈德堡'''（{{lang-en|Dave Goldberg}}，{{bd|1967年|10月2日|2015年|5月1日}}）是一位企业管理顾问和商人，是{{link-en|LAUNCH Media|LAUNCH Media}}的创始人和[[SurveyMonkey|SurveyMonkey]]的首席执行官，同时也是[[Facebook|Facebook]][[首席运营官|首席运营官]][[雪莉·桑德伯格|雪莉·桑德伯格]]的丈夫。

==早期生活和教育经历==
戈德堡1967年10月2日出生于伊利诺伊州芝加哥并于[[明尼苏达州|明尼苏达州]][[明尼阿波利斯|明尼阿波利斯]]长大<ref name="WP obit">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/david-goldberg-executive-of-online-questionnaire-service-dies-at-47/2015/05/02/a3ded996-f112-11e4-8abc-d6aa3bad79dd_story.html|title=David Goldberg, 47, SurveyMonkey CEO, Sandberg Husband, Dies|last=Coppola|first=Gabrielle|first2=Sarah|last2=Frier|date=May 2, 2015|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=November 5, 2015|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010113930/https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/david-goldberg-executive-of-online-questionnaire-service-dies-at-47/2015/05/02/a3ded996-f112-11e4-8abc-d6aa3bad79dd_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的母亲宝拉·戈德堡是Pacer Center的联合创始人，他的父亲梅尔·戈德堡（1942——1998）是{{link-en|威廉·米切尔法学院|William Mitchell College of Law}}的副院长和教授<ref name="WP obit" />。他高中时，在明尼阿波利斯''Star Tribune''报纸实习过<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/david-goldberg-surveymonkey-ceo-dies-at-age-47-1430672009 |title=Web Executive David Goldberg Dies at Age 47 |publisher=''The Wall Street Journal'' |subscription=yes |date=May 3, 2015 |accessdate=May 4, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108162028/https://www.wsj.com/articles/david-goldberg-surveymonkey-ceo-dies-at-age-47-1430672009 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1985年，戈德堡从明尼阿波利斯的{{link-en|布莱克学校|Blake School (Minneapolis)}}毕业<ref name="Star-Trib">{{cite news|url=http://www.startribune.com/local/302317551.html|title=David Goldberg, Silicon Valley CEO with deep ties to Minneapolis, dies at 47|date=May 3, 2015|work=Minneapolis Star-Tribune|accessdate=May 3, 2015|archive-date=2015-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505015025/http://www.startribune.com/local/302317551.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1989年，他以优等成绩从[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]毕业，主修历史和政治<ref name=nytimes/>。戈德堡一生都是[[明尼苏达维京人|明尼苏达维京人]]队的忠实粉丝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Grant|first1=Adam|title=Remembering Dave Goldberg, the Ultimate Mensch|url=https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/remembering-dave-goldberg-ultimate-mensch-adam-grant|accessdate=May 23, 2015|work=[[Pulse_(app)|Pulse]]|publisher=LinkedIn|date=May 10, 2015|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907025302/https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/remembering-dave-goldberg-ultimate-mensch-adam-grant|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==职业生涯==
毕业之后，戈德堡在[[贝恩策略顾问|贝恩策略顾问]]工作了两年。他本打算之后去攻读法学院，但是最后转而加入了[[国会唱片|国会唱片]]担任市场战略经理并负责拓展新业务<ref>{{cite news|last1=Swisher|first1=Kara|title=Former Yahoo Music Exec Dave Goldberg to Head SurveyMonkey|url=http://allthingsd.com/20090420/former-yahoo-music-exec-dave-goldberg-to-head-survey-monkey/|accessdate=May 4, 2015|publisher=All Things D|date=April 20, 2009|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504211623/http://allthingsd.com/20090420/former-yahoo-music-exec-dave-goldberg-to-head-survey-monkey/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=businessinsider>{{cite news|last1=Bort|first1=Julie|title=Dave Goldberg had an incredible life — but it wasn't easy|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/the-incredible-life-of-david-goldberg-2015-5|accessdate=May 3, 2015|work=Business Insider|date=May 2, 2015|archive-date=2019-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220114156/https://www.businessinsider.com/the-incredible-life-of-david-goldberg-2015-5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1994年，他创立了{{link-en|LAUNCH Media|LAUNCH Media}}，该公司于2001年被[[雅虎|雅虎]]收购。戈德堡之后于2007年离开了雅虎并加入了
风险投资公司{{link-en|Benchmark Capital|Benchmark (venture capital firm)}}。2009年，他加入了[[SurveyMonkey|SurveyMonkey]]任首席执行官<ref name=nytimes/>。

==个人生活==
2004年，戈德堡和雪莉·桑德伯格结婚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eyerys.com/articles/people/passion-and-contribution-inside-social-elite-sheryl-sandberg|title=The Passion And Contribution Inside The Social Elite By Sheryl Sandberg|work=Eyerys|date=November 25, 2015|access-date=2015-12-25|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202234320/https://www.eyerys.com/articles/people/passion-and-contribution-inside-social-elite-sheryl-sandberg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他们共有两个孩子<ref name=nytimes />。

==死亡和纪念活动==
2015年5月1日，戈德堡和桑德伯格前往墨西哥度假，并入住{{link-en|蓬塔米塔|Punta Mita}}的[[四季酒店|四季酒店]]。依据[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]检察官办公室的说法，他在健身馆运动时意外地从[[跑步机|跑步机]]上跌落，头部受损且出血。当天稍晚些时候，他在{{link-en|努埃沃尔塔|Nuevo Vallarta}}的一家医院离世<ref name=nytimes>{{cite web|last1=Goel|first1=Vindu|last2=Hardy|first2=Quentin|title=Dave Goldberg, Head of Web Survey Company and Half of a Silicon Valley Power Couple, Dies at 47|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/03/business/dave-goldberg-47-surveymonkey-chief-and-sheryl-sandbergs-husband-dies.html|work=The New York Times|accessdate=May 2, 2015|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308180315/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/03/business/dave-goldberg-47-surveymonkey-chief-and-sheryl-sandbergs-husband-dies.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Goel|first1=Vindu|title=Dave Goldberg, Silicon Valley Executive, Said to Have Died After Exercising|url=http://nyti.ms/1KHa9Yq|work=The New York Times|accessdate=May 4, 2015|last2=Archibold|first2=Randal C.}}</ref><ref name="BBCaccident">{{cite news
